{"type":"message","id":"250b5849","parentId":"4bd72f8a","timestamp":"2026-02-23T13:14:51.590Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"                 functions.read:33","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-02-10 - Skills Inventory Complete\n\n## Task: Catalog Project Skills\n\nScanned and inventorized 115 skills from `/home/project/openclaw/skills/`.\n\n### Created Artifacts\n\n1. **Catalog**: `memory/skills-catalog.json`\n   - Full JSON inventory with categories, subcategories, purposes\n   - Use-case keyword mapping (send_email вҶ’ gmail-automation, etc.)\n   - Skill index for fast lookup\n\n2. **Search Script**: `scripts/skill-search.py`\n   - `skill-search.py <query>` вҖ” keyword search\n   - `skill-search.py --recommend \"<task>\"` вҖ” task-based recommendations\n   - `skill-search.py --category <cat>` вҖ” list by category\n   - `skill-search.py --use-case <uc>` вҖ” find by use case\n   - `skill-search.py --detail <skill>` вҖ” show SKILL.md preview\n   - `skill-search.py --list` вҖ” show all categories\n\n### Skill Categories (9 total)\n\n| Category | Count | Description |\n|----------|-------|-------------|\n| app_automation | 78 | SaaS apps via Rube MCP (Composio) |\n| development | 11 | Coding, DevOps, development tools |\n| creative_media | 6 | Design, visual art, media |\n| business_marketing | 5 | Sales, marketing, BI |\n| productivity | 5 | Organization, workflow |\n\n[16 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771852491587}}
{"type":"message","id":"0436822d","parentId":"250b5849","timestamp":"2026-02-23T13:14:51.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"                 functions.read:34","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-02-18 - Daily Notes\n\n## Morning\n\n### 7:08 AM вҖ” Gateway Token Issue\n- User reported missing 7 AM daily ping (cron job)\n- Investigated: **device token mismatch** in gateway auth\n- **Root cause:** systemd service had stale token in memory from previous config update\n- **Fix:** `systemctl --user daemon-reload && systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service`\n- Gateway now healthy, RPC probe: ok\n- Cron system operational, but missed today's run\n\n### 9:53 AM вҖ” Manual Daily Ping Trigger\n- Gateway confirmed operational\n- Fetched Bitcoin: $67,078 (вҶ“2.51%)\n- Fetched stock prices: NVDA $184.98, MSFT $396.79, GOOGL $302.01, INTC $46.21, META $639.27, AMD $203.04\n- Fetched GitHub top repos via API\n- Sent daily ping to Telegram topic 1087368827 вң…\n\n### 10:44 AM вҖ” Config Update Requested\n- User requested to lock all API calls to NVIDIA provider only\n- Updated `/home/pete/.openclaw/openclaw.json`:\n  - Removed other auth profiles (openai, moonshot, openrouter)\n  - Retained only `nvidia:default` provider\n  - Kept existing NVIDIA config with moonshotai/kimi-k2.5 model\n- Still need to restart gateway to apply changes\n\n---\n\n## Afternoon\n\n### 4:18 PM вҖ” Persona & Skills Recap\n- User requested full persona recap\n- **WHOAMI.md created:** `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/WHOAMI.md`\n  - Core persona (lobster energy, direct communication, actual opinions)\n  - Roles (trusty assistant, coding assistant, frontend architect, proactive operator)\n  - Standard Operating Procedure (ANALYZE вҶ’ PLAN вҶ’ VALIDATE вҶ’ IMPLEMENT вҶ’ VERIFY вҶ’ DELIVER)\n  - Skills inventory: ~125 skills across categories + 11 knowledge work plugins\n\n### 5:05 PM вҖ” PRD Understanding Request\n- User requested analysis of `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/PRD.md`\n- **UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md created:** `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md`\n  - Architecture philosophy (SQLite, vectors, Telegram-first)\n  - CRM system deep dive (~1,174 contacts, 16 intent types, discovery pipeline)\n  - Skills inventory (22 installed + 2 preview)\n  - Critical tools (cron-log, business-meta-analysis, social-tracker)\n  - Database inventory (15+ databases)\n  - Cron jobs (30+ scheduled tasks)\n  - Key operational patterns\n\n---\n\n## Reference Files Created Today\n\n| File | Purpose | Location |\n|------|---------|----------|\n| **WHOAMI.md** | Persona, roles, responsibilities, skills inventory | `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/WHOAMI.md` |\n| **UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md** | Architecture guide, CRM system, operational patterns | `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md` |\n\n---\n\n## Pending Items\n\n- [ ] Restart gateway to apply NVIDIA-only config changes\n- [ ] Verify daily ping resumes tomorrow (7 AM Asia/Singapore)\n\n---\n\n*Written by trusty-pal рҹӨқрҹҰһ*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771852491597}}
